text: Midkiff is an unincorporated community in western Lincoln County, West Virginia, United States. Its elevation is 597 feet (182 m)., Geographic Names Information System, 1980-06-27. Accessed 2008-03-29. Although it is unincorporated, it has a post office, with the ZIP code of 25540. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in West Virginia
title: Midkiff, West Virginia
